{"tid":2021281,"cid":14,"subCid":0,"title":"23-24號國寶大罷工","createTime":"2020-05-17T15:34:49.000Z","updateTime":"2020-05-17T17:16:35.000Z","uid":20164,"like":2,"dislike":2,"uniUserReply":3,"replies":[{"pid":"9303f35f41d9a22bd7bd06c4557768fe9e190b6b","tid":2021281,"uid":20164,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-05-17T15:34:49.000Z","msg":"23-24號國寶大罷工<br />\n目的：要公司正視佢地既系統，ＣＳ，政策及人工<br />\n行動：拎哂所有更，及準時上線。有單就接，接完唔洗去拎餐！！！<br />\n分析：餐廳做完餐，公司就要比錢間餐廳。外賣員唔去送，只係停３０分鐘，而餐廳係無損失。<br />\n<br />\n放棄兩日人工，換到之後既人道處理，步兵唔洗再做電單車單，步兵舒服，車手有單。大家人工齊齊加，歡迎大家齊齊搶更，特別係第五組人士，更加無任何大影響。"},{"pid":"5a85b0d7501a280f43e7cb1411db5541a65bb9e0","tid":2021281,"uid":20164,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-05-17T15:35:14.000Z","msg":"自推10次<br />\n1"},{"pid":"9d43c0d92ea653ed50b568a47c64dd71dd45fdd7","tid":2021281,"uid":20164,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-05-17T15:35:25.000Z","msg":"2"},{"pid":"e2618c5d539416b09560e18999f66a0d36bb2a86","tid":2021281,"uid":20164,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-05-17T15:35:35.000Z","msg":"3"},{"pid":"c555b64bf97aba9cb0ab1fb8481397f1c6599cf0","tid":2021281,"uid":20164,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-05-17T15:35:45.000Z","msg":"4"},{"pid":"fa3beae1ce011a4859aa14a0c2d0f704a915632e","tid":2021281,"uid":20164,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-05-17T15:35:55.000Z","msg":"5"},{"pid":"4f7593a74b5b783fd26ed88c61e771e60affa70b","tid":2021281,"uid":20164,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-05-17T15:36:05.000Z","msg":"6"},{"pid":"cd96bc72cfbc99c68c55e7986a3f0764a560e560","tid":2021281,"uid":20164,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-05-17T15:36:15.000Z","msg":"7"},{"pid":"d4920ee12199e1690e3618b6eeea0242cad08715","tid":2021281,"uid":20164,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-05-17T15:36:25.000Z","msg":"8"},{"pid":"4468bd76c032b4636480a48e018c6c7968e59b2d","